00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:10,140
It's just a nucleus.

180
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:17,140
It's just a nucleus and a bunch of electrons.

181
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:18,640
And what I'm actually interested

