00:20:49,140 --> 00:20:50,140
Short wavelengths,

484
00:20:50,140 --> 00:20:52,140
entail high frequencies.

485
00:20:52,140 --> 00:20:54,140
And so the things that we're getting rid of

486
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:56,140
in the problem are

487
00:20:56,140 --> 00:20:58,140
the degrees of freedom associated with

488
00:20:58,140 --> 00:21:00,140
very high energies,

489
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:01,140
very high frequencies.

