00:21:55,140 --> 00:21:58,140
But it still leaves one dimension

514
00:21:58,140 --> 00:21:59,140
that you have to specify,

515
00:21:59,140 --> 00:22:01,140
one dimension that you need,

516
00:22:01,140 --> 00:22:03,140
one quantity with dimensions.

