01:04:13,686 --> 01:04:16,186
So what's going on is the

1499
01:04:16,186 --> 01:04:18,686
effect of very small distance physics

1500
01:04:18,686 --> 01:04:20,186
when you sum it all up

1501
01:04:20,186 --> 01:04:21,686
and take it all into account

1502
01:04:21,686 --> 01:04:24,686
the same way we took the electrons into account

1503
01:04:24,686 --> 01:04:26,686
when we studied...

1504
01:04:27,686 --> 01:04:30,686
molecules, for example.

1505
01:04:30,686 --> 01:04:32,686
We take them into account, we solve

1506
01:04:32,686 --> 01:04:34,686
