01:04:59,686 --> 01:05:01,686
That's the main lesson.

1516
01:05:01,686 --> 01:05:03,686
The parameters of the theory you measure

1517
01:05:03,686 --> 01:05:06,186
are those which take into account all the short

1518
01:05:06,186 --> 01:05:08,686
distance physics on scales smaller than you can see.

